  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Infant care Teacher",
  "description": "<p>Join Our Team of Dedicated Infant Care Educators! 👶🌟</p><p>Are you passionate about caring for and nurturing the tiniest members of our community? We're searching for compassionate and skilled infant care teachers and assistants to be a part of our team! 👩‍🏫🍼🧡</p><p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>ACEY Certification</li><li>HCIC Certification</li><li>Relevant Infant Care Certification</li></ul><p><strong>Job Roles:</strong></p><ul><li>Infant Routine Care</li><li>Conducting Engaging Activities</li><li>Preparing Thoughtful Lesson Plans</li><li>Completing Developmental Checklists and Portfolios</li></ul><p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p><ul><li>Supportive Management Team</li><li>Comprehensive Training Provided</li><li>Career Progression Opportunity</li><li>Meals Provided</li></ul><p>If you have a deep love for infants and are eager to contribute to their early development, we encourage you to apply! 🍼🎨✨</p><p>Those who are interested to join the early childhood industry but do not have the relevant certifications or experience may apply too.</p><p>Ready to embark on a fulfilling journey with us? Please send your resume to macpherson@cambridge.school or contact us at 83506156 to explore this fantastic opportunity</p>",
